</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_103_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ıeber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>ıben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>ſalma<ex>n</ex></expan> teẅfels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des Juden etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l3">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> erfaren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l4">daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> teẅfel Jud bey vns niht ıſt vnd in <expan>lang<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒeıt bey vns niht <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l5">ıſt als vns dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo ıſt auch er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> noch der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l6">nıht <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd noch niht ıſt / Vnd wo wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l8">Otten <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_103" id="50v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
