<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Steͣtemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu
                        Lawden </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                <expan>Salma<ex>n</ex></expan> Tewfels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des juden etc.,
            das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> erfaren, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Tewfel jud
            bey uns niht ist und in <expan>lang<ex>er</ex></expan> zeit bey uns niht
                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, als uns die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
            gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. So ist auch er <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> noch der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> niht
                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> und noch niht ist, und wo wir
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Otten,
                <expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
